<p>Suppose I created a program in C.  How to establish communications between the C program &amp; other PHP Program.</p>  <p>For Example C program is to draw geometry figures. upon execution it asks.</p>  <p>Select which on to draw:</p>  <ol> <li>Rectangle</li> <li>Circle</li> <li>Triangle</li> </ol>  <p>command-Line I type: 1</p>  <p>Then the program ask length and breadth:</p>  <p>length: 10</p>  <p>breadth: 11</p>